snippet.title: Osiris: New Dawn (Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
After crash-landing on an distant planet, build a colony with your friends, battle others and explore the system prospecting for immeasurable riches. In Osiris: New Dawn, discover, fight, and tame indigenous alien creatures or search for lost human expeditions as you survive the far reaches of space.
